00:16:39.492 --> 00:16:44.042
of the money that they have spent in the past, thinking that if they haven’t won anything for

00:16:44.052 --> 00:16:49.846
months, their numbers are bound to come up soon and they will be able to recoup their losses.

00:16:51.376 --> 00:16:54.326
